data.description: Ranch home on over 1/2 acre close to I-394 for easy Chicago commute. Custom built with over 2,500 ft2 on one level: NO STAIRS.  Circular drive offers plenty of parking in addition to attached 2 car garage. Not your cookie cutter home! The family room is going to sell this home: vaulted ceilings, brick fireplace, unique wood lined skylights, custom ceiling heat blowers & wood beams. Large kitchen (TONS of cabinets & counter space). Cozy breakfast nook over looks the spacious yard. Owner wants to down size, this house is simply just too much space. Property could also be commercial (seller talked w/local officials who are receptive to rezoning).  "AGENTS AND/OR PERSPECTIVE BUYERS EXPOSED TO COVID 19 OR WITH A COUGH OR FEVER ARE NOT TO ENTER THE HOME UNTIL THEY RECEIVE MEDICAL CLEARANCE."
